'''''Pumzi''''' ni film ngufi ya siyanse y'impimbano yo muri Kenya yanditswe kandi iyobowe na Wanuri Kahiu<ref>Pumzi / Air | African Film Festival, Inc. <nowiki>https://africanfilmny.org</nowiki> › films › pumzi</ref> . Yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sundance 2010 mu rwego rwa gahunda yayo nshya ya Afurika<ref>Kenyan Sci-Fi Short Pumzi Hits Sundance With Dystopia <nowiki>https://www.wired.com</nowiki> › Culture › Movies</ref>.    Uyu mushinga watewe inkunga  n’ikigega cy’ubuhanzi cya Changamoto, ndetse n’ikigo cya Goethe Institut na Focus Features <ref>Pumzi - Into Film <nowiki>https://www.intofilm.org</nowiki> › films</ref>. Kahiu yizeye kwagura bigufi muburyo bwuzuye<ref>Pumzi | Festival International de Films de Fribourg <nowiki>https://www.fiff.ch</nowiki> › pumzi</ref>.  Filime iri mucyongereza,  ariko umutwe ni [[Igiswahili]] bisobanuye"Umwuka"<ref>Pumzi | 31st Cascade Festival of African Films <nowiki>https://www.africanfilmfestival.org</nowiki> › festival › pumzi</ref>. 

=== Afurika ===
Pumzi igwa cyane mubwoko bwa Africanfuturism <ref>Afro-futurism and the aesthetics of hope in Bekolo's Les ... <nowiki>https://www.tandfonline.com</nowiki> › ... › Volume 10, Issue 2</ref>. Irerekana uko ejo hazaza hazaba umuco (uherereye kumugabane wa Afrika) utuwe cyane nabirabura<ref>Afrofuturism Imagines: Water Wars - Girls in Film <nowiki>https://www.girlsinfilm.net</nowiki> › post › afrofuturism-imagin...</ref>. Byongeye kandi, yakozwe na sitidiyo yo muri Afrika yepfo igizwe nitsinda ryabashinzwe gukora no kumenyekanisha uburyo bushya bwibintu ndangamuco biva mubihugu bya Afrika<ref>Films: Pumzi and Scheherazade Tell Me a Story - The Africa ... <nowiki>https://www.theafricareport.com</nowiki> › films-pumzi-and-sch...</ref>. ''Pumzi'' ihuza neza na motif ikunze kuboneka muri Africanfuturism , ariko ntibigarukiraho gusa, kuba hari ahantu nyaburanga hatagira uruhare runini rw'amazi<ref>Pumzi (DVD video, 2009) [WorldCat.org] <nowiki>https://www.worldcat.org</nowiki> › title › pumzi › oclc</ref>.
